com.gmail.etordera.jcms

Class JCMS

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gmail.etordera.jcms.JCMS

  • public class JCMS
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class for the JavaCMS library.

    Defines common constants and provides JNI access to LittleCMS library.

      • cmsCreateTransform

        public static long cmsCreateTransform(long hInputProfile,
                      int inputFormat,
                      long hOutputProfile,
                      int outputFormat,
                      int intent,
                      int flags)
        Creates a color transform for translating bitmaps.
        Parameters:
        hInputProfile - Handle to a profile object capable to work in input direction
        inputFormat - Input bitmap buffer type identifier (TYPE_*)
        hOutputProfile - Handle to a profile object capable to work in output direction
        outputFormat - Output bitmap buffer type identifier (TYPE_*)
        intent - Intent identifier (INTENT_*)
        flags - Bit-field constants for the conversion (CMSFLAGS_*)
        Returns:
        A handle to a transform object on success, 0 on error.

        Parameters:
        hTransform - Handle to the transform object to be freed.
